    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SokoMage</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271380/extras/974c7c7996828b359bccbfdbe2b6a83d.poster.avif?t=1728298298\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271380/extras/974c7c7996828b359bccbfdbe2b6a83d.webm?t=1728298298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271380/extras/974c7c7996828b359bccbfdbe2b6a83d.mp4?t=1728298298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stop Pads - Stops the rock from moving regardless of the incoming direction</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Directional Pads - Redirects the rock to the facing direction of the arrow</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271380/extras/8deb274508a889bd54d95c52712182d1.poster.avif?t=1728298298\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271380/extras/8deb274508a889bd54d95c52712182d1.webm?t=1728298298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271380/extras/8deb274508a889bd54d95c52712182d1.mp4?t=1728298298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 30 levels to explore. You choose!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Many ways to complete the same puzzle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Beautiful pixel graphics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Captivating and interesting puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The controls are simple and accessible.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
